Interface HttpRequestProcessor

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultHttpRequestProcessor, PeerChannelHttpRequestProcessor, PeerHttpConnectRequestProcessor, PeerHttpRequestProcessor
public interface HttpRequestProcessor

Processor for HTTP requests. Different implementations might go to peers or other forms of proxies, or even reply directly through a cache.
